## SteamApi

### Batch Steam Profile
## Batch Steam Profile
GET https://api.deadlock-api.com/v1/players/steam?accountIds={{accountIds}}&refresh={{refresh}}
Accept: application/json

### Steam Profile Search
## Steam Profile Search
GET https://api.deadlock-api.com/v1/players/steam-search?searchQuery={{searchQuery}}&limit={{limit}}&minMatchesPlayedLast30d={{minMatchesPlayedLast30d}}&minLastTeamAvgBadge={{minLastTeamAvgBadge}}&matchesPlayedWeight={{matchesPlayedWeight}}
Accept: application/json
